            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Easy Targets</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Exposed wiring in walls</li>
              <li>• Spools left unsecured</li>
              <li>• Predictable locations</li>
              <li>• Weekend vulnerability</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-orange-50 rounded">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-orange-800">70% of thefts occur on weekends</p>
            </div>
