                <li>Material storage yards covered 24/7</li>
                <li>Gang boxes and tool storage monitored</li>
                <li>Active work areas under surveillance</li>
                <li>Perimeter breach detection</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Layer 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-xl">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Advanced Detection Technology</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Thermal and AI-powered cameras detect suspicious activity even in complete darkness.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>Thermal imaging sees heat signatures at night</li>
                <li>AI distinguishes workers from intruders</li>
                <li>Motion zones around high-value materials</li>
                <li>License plate capture at entry/exit</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Layer 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <div class="bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-xl">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Instant Alert & Response</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Real-time monitoring with immediate intervention when threats detected.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>Motion alerts to monitoring center in seconds</li>
                <li>Live audio warnings through speakers</li>
                <li>Strobe lights activate to disorient thieves</li>
                <li>Site manager notified immediately</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Layer 4 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <div class="bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-xl">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Law Enforcement Coordination</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Direct connection to police with verified video for priority response.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>Verified crime in progress = faster response</li>
                <li>Real-time suspect descriptions provided</li>
                <li>Video evidence for immediate arrest</li>
                <li>Prosecution support with clear footage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Layer 5 -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <div class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-xl">5</div>
