            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-red-600">Threat:</p>
                <p>3 nearby sites hit for $200K+ copper theft</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-green-600">Action:</p>
                <p>Deployed 3 trailers covering electrical storage</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Result:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700">
                  <li>2 attempted thefts stopped</li>
                  <li>Both crews arrested on-site</li>
