              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded">
                <p class="text-sm"><span class="font-bold">Quote:</span> "The trailers paid for themselves in the first prevented theft" - Project Manager</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Success Story 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-orange-600 text-white p-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Data Center Build - Kent Valley</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-red-600">Threat:</p>
                <p>$2M+ in copper wire on-site, high-crime area</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-green-600">Action:</p>
                <p>4-trailer system with thermal cameras</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="font-semibold text-blue-600">Result:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700">
                  <li>5 intrusion attempts detected</li>
                  <li>All fled when warned via audio</li>
                  <li>100% materials protected</li>
                  <li>25% insurance discount earned</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded">
                <p class="text-sm"><span class="font-bold">Savings:</span> $2M protected, $50K insurance savings</p>
              </div>
