          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-900">Average ROI for Copper Theft Prevention</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">850% Return</div>
          <p class="text-gray-700">One prevented theft saves 10x the monthly surveillance cost</p>
        </div>
      </div>
