        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Protect Your Copper Before Tonight's Theft</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Every unprotected night is a risk. Thieves are watching. Get surveillance deployed today.</p>
